Installation:
  
    git clone git://github.com/murilomonteiro/vimfiles.git $HOME/.vim

Create symLinks:

    ln -s $HOME/vimfiles/vimrc $HOME/.vimrc
    ln -s $HOME/vimfiles/gvimrc $HOME/.gvimrc

Include plugins:

    Just clone a repository inside of bundle directory, pathogen automatic load plugins for you.

Update Script:
  
    Put the update_vim_bundles in your $PATH and you can update all submodules in your bundle for you.

    git clone git://github.com/taq/vim-bundles-updater


